WEBVTT

00:00.015 --> 00:01.196
Previously on
<i>Suits...</i>

00:01.197 --> 00:02.225
This is a copy of the letter

00:02.226 --> 00:03.425
you wrote a copy
to the district attorney

00:03.426 --> 00:04.993
when you threatened
expose me.

00:04.994 --> 00:07.470
You ever do send that letter,
you're in the same boat as me.

00:07.471 --> 00:08.638
You want to move in here?

00:08.706 --> 00:11.408
I've only ever
been here twice,

00:11.475 --> 00:13.493
and both times
were with you.

00:13.577 --> 00:15.257
You beat me
on the dissolution negotiation,

00:15.279 --> 00:16.439
you get your name
on the door.

00:16.447 --> 00:17.314
If you think you're gonna win
this time,

00:17.381 --> 00:18.632
you've got another thing
coming.

00:18.716 --> 00:20.083
You ready to use
your relationship with Rachel

00:20.151 --> 00:21.451
to get her father to turn?

00:21.519 --> 00:23.153
Doesn't matter,
because I'm not gonna do that.

00:23.220 --> 00:25.155
Folsom Foods.
This is about Harvey Specter,

00:25.222 --> 00:27.691
Jessica Pearson,
and their divorce negotiations,

00:27.758 --> 00:29.059
and you don't go to the one
you didn't marry

00:29.126 --> 00:30.326
to stick it
to the one you did.

00:30.361 --> 00:31.561
It's a check
from Folsom Foods.

00:31.562 --> 00:33.163
It's the remainder
of what they owe us.

00:33.230 --> 00:35.365
If you crush me,
I'll have nothing.

00:35.433 --> 00:36.399
He was bullying me.

00:36.467 --> 00:38.101
So you used me
to bully him back.

00:38.169 --> 00:39.052
If you don't want
to live with me,

00:39.136 --> 00:40.103
why don't you just tell me?

00:40.171 --> 00:41.504
I just need some time.

00:41.572 --> 00:43.606
- Hessington Oil just fired us.
- Scottie betrayed me.

00:43.674 --> 00:45.408
I gave you my word,
and I honored it.

00:45.476 --> 00:46.943
Something dropped
from the sky,

00:47.011 --> 00:49.179
tilted everything in your favor
right after I cut you a break?

00:49.246 --> 00:51.798
I am not going to dissolve
this merger.

00:51.882 --> 00:52.816
You already signed
the agreement.

00:52.883 --> 00:54.183
Then sue me.

00:54.235 --> 00:56.319
Scottie didn't get us fired.
Ava Hessington did.

00:56.387 --> 00:58.088
She's suing all of us.

00:58.155 --> 01:00.023
I got into Stanford.

01:02.000 --> 01:08.074
